description: Coastal charm meets modern city living in this beautifully updated top-floor condo, just 1.5 blocks from South Boston’s coveted shoreline. This sunlit deeded three-bed, two-bath home is currently arranged as a spacious two-bed for effortless entertaining and everyday comfort. The open-concept layout features a stylish kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a glass-tile backsplash, and a granite island that flows seamlessly into a living room and wainscoted dining area—perfect for hosting or unwinding after a beach day. The primary suite offers a bright bay window, walk-in closet, and a sleek en-suite bath with a tiled shower. A private back deck with views of Telegraph Hill, in-unit laundry, generous basement storage, and exclusive roof rights with harbor-view potential make this home a rare find. Nestled in one of Southie’s most desirable neighborhoods, enjoy easy access to the shoreline, parks, and restaurants. Ideal for city dwellers craving a coastal retreat or savvy investors!
